						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up near the sluice of a tank.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Nṛipatuṅgappōttaraiyar year 6:</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription is engraved carelessly and records the construction of a sluice at Vaḻugūr by Aṟamiḷippāru Vaḷagū[r*] of Maṉṉarmaṅgalam in Taḻundūr-nāḍu.</p>						

						<p>(Published in <hi rend="italic">S.I.I.,</hi> Vol. XII, No. 62). </p>						

